Interface RandomDataProvider<T>

All Superinterfaces:
DataProvider<T>
All Known Subinterfaces:
RandomNumberProvider<T>, RandomStringProvider
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractRandomDataProvider, AbstractRandomNumberProvider, DefaultRandomStringProvider, RandomDoubleProvider, RandomFloatProvider, RandomIntegerProvider, RandomLongProvider
public interface RandomDataProvider<T>
extends DataProvider<T>

Provides random data. Random generators will provide configuration methods which again return self-references to build up chained-call configuration.
